 of infinitely many heteroclinic orbits.\nAdditional equilibria exist in Sandstede's model and we compactify phase space\nto capture how equilibria may emerge from or escape to infinity. We present\nimages of these bifurcation diagrams, where we outline different configurations\nof equilibria close to homoclinic flip bifurcations of case $\\textbf{B}$;\nfurthermore, we characterize the dynamics of Sandstede's model at infinity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 28 Jul 2022 01:27:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-29"}
